The paper deals with the problem of recommendation systems, which is a subfield of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of latent factor models and Markov chains suggests that the paper may also fall under machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The development of efficient algorithms and parallel multi-core implementation suggests that the paper may also belong to the subfields of systems and control (cs.SI) and databases (cs.DB).
